The Glenn Beck Show PODCAST SEP-30-2013 MON





The Glenn Beck Program - 09/30/13


Monday, September 30, 2013 10:28 AM


The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,


Glenn and the crew discuss Obamacare and the impending government shutdown.

 Also, Fox News host and author Bill O'Reilly joins the show to talk about
